::ProjectionFieldNotOnValueClassError
  |~~ Projection segment is not a publicly-projectable field on the value-class subject (Quote / Doc / вЂ¦). ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ProjectionIndexOutOfBoundsError
  |~~ Projection `/n` вЂ” the integer index resolves outside the Vec subject's `[0, length)` range. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ProjectionKeyNotInMapError
  |~~ Projection `/key` вЂ” the named key is absent from the Map subject (strict-miss). Use `at(:key)` for null-coalescing access. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ProjectionSubjectNotMapError
  |~~ Projection `/key` requires a Map, Vec, or value-class subject; null subject and other shapes lift to this error. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ProjectionVecKeyNotIntegerError
  |~~ Projection segment is a non-numeric string but the subject is a Vec вЂ” Vec indices must be integer offsets. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Combinator track-dispatch throws в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::DistributeSubjectNotVecError
  |~~ Distribute combinator (`*`) вЂ” subject must be a Vec for per-element forking. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::MergeSubjectNotVecError
  |~~ Merge combinator (`>>`) вЂ” subject must be a Vec for one-level flattening. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Type-binding (::tag / ::conduit) throws в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::TypeBindingHasNoConstructorError
  |~~ `::tag` constructor invocation failed вЂ” the type-binding's `:qlang/impl` is neither a primitive Keyword nor a Quote. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::TaggedLitNotTypeError
  |~~ `::tag` constructor invocation failed вЂ” the env binding under `::tag` is not a type-binding descriptor Map. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::TaggedLitTagNotFoundError
  |~~ `::tag` constructor invocation failed вЂ” the tag is not a registered type-binding in env. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ConduitArityMismatchError
  |~~ Conduit invocation supplied a captured-arg count different from the conduit's declared parameter list. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ConduitBodyMissingSourceError
  |~~ `makeConduit` refuses a body AST that has no `.text` source slice вЂ” `printValue` round-trip would otherwise emit a non-parseable placeholder. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ConduitParameterNoCapturedArgsError
  |~~ Conduit-parameter proxies are nullary вЂ” passing captured arguments to a parameter reference raises this error. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Identifier-lookup + effect-laundering throws в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::EffectLaunderingAtBindStepParseError
  |~~ BindStep declaration body references an `@`-effectful identifier, but the binding name itself is not `@`-prefixed вЂ” laundering caught at parse time. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ApplyToNonFunctionError
  |~~ Identifier resolves to a non-function value вЂ” captured arguments cannot be applied. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::EffectLaunderingAtCallError
  |~~ Identifier resolves to an `@`-effectful function, but the lookup name is not `@`-prefixed вЂ” laundering caught at the call site. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::UnresolvedIdentifierError
  |~~ Identifier lookup failed вЂ” no env binding under that name. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Parser throws в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::ParseError
  |~~ Parser failure вЂ” source did not match the grammar. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ AST / value codec throws в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::AstMapKindUnknownError
  |~~ AST-Map в†’ AST codec вЂ” `:qlang/kind` discriminator names a kind the codec does not know. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::AstMapMalformedError
  |~~ AST-Map в†’ AST codec вЂ” input Map is malformed (missing required field, wrong shape). ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::AstNodeTypeUnknownError
  |~~ AST в†’ AST-Map codec вЂ” encountered an AST node whose `.type` is not in the codec's known shape table. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::MalformedTaggedJSONError
  |~~ `fromTaggedJSON` received a JSON shape it does not recognise as a tagged-value envelope. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::TaggedJSONUnencodableValueError
  |~~ `toTaggedJSON` cannot encode a function / conduit / snapshot value вЂ” use `serializeSession` for the binding-aware path. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Evaluator + Rule 10 dispatch invariants в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::HigherOrderOpArityMismatchError
  |~~ Dispatch invariant вЂ” `higherOrderOp` impl received an unexpected captured-arg count. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::HigherOrderOpVariadicMissingCapturedError
  |~~ Dispatch invariant вЂ” `higherOrderOpVariadic` registration is missing the `captured` range argument. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::NullaryOpArgsProvidedError
  |~~ Dispatch invariant вЂ” nullary operand received captured arguments. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::OverloadedOpUnsupportedArityError
  |~~ Dispatch invariant вЂ” overloaded operand has no impl for the supplied captured-arg count. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::StateOpArityMismatchError
  |~~ Dispatch invariant вЂ” `stateOp` impl received an unexpected captured-arg count. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::StateOpVariadicMissingCapturedError
  |~~ Dispatch invariant вЂ” `stateOpVariadic` registration is missing the `captured` range argument. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ValueOpArityMismatchError
  |~~ Dispatch invariant вЂ” `valueOp` impl received an unexpected captured-arg count for its declared arity. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::UnknownAstNodeTypeError
  |~~ Evaluator dispatch вЂ” encountered an AST node whose `.type` is not in `AST_NODE_EVALUATORS`. Runtime invariant violation, never reaches user code. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::UnknownCombinatorKindError
  |~~ Combinator dispatch вЂ” encountered a combinator kind not in `COMBINATOR_EVALUATORS`. Runtime invariant violation. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::Rule10ArityOverflowError
  |~~ Rule 10 вЂ” operand call supplied more captured arguments than the operand's declared maximum arity. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Primitive-registry invariants в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::PrimitiveKeyAlreadyBoundError
  |~~ Primitive registry вЂ” two runtime modules tried to bind the same primitive name. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::PrimitiveKeyNotStringError
  |~~ Primitive registry вЂ” bind() received a non-string handle. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::PrimitiveKeyUnboundError
  |~~ Primitive registry вЂ” `:qlang/impl` handle on a descriptor Map points to a primitive that was never bound. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::PrimitiveRegistrySealedError
  |~~ Primitive registry вЂ” bind() called after the registry was sealed at langRuntime bootstrap. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Session-codec throws в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::SessionBindingKindUnknownError
  |~~ Session deserialization вЂ” a binding entry carries an unknown `:kind`. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::SessionConduitSourceMissingError
  |~~ Session deserialization вЂ” a conduit binding entry has no `:source` to re-parse. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::SessionPayloadInvalidError
  |~~ Session deserialization вЂ” payload is malformed (missing required fields). ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::SessionSchemaVersionMismatchError
  |~~ Session deserialization вЂ” payload `:schemaVersion` does not match the current SESSION_SCHEMA_VERSION. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Render invariants в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::FunctionValueLeakedToPrintError
  |~~ `printValue` / `toPlain` invariant вЂ” a raw function value reached render. Wrap host operands in a descriptor Map carrying `:qlang/kind :builtin` and `:qlang/impl` instead of binding the function via `session.bind`. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

|~ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Misc throws в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ~|

::ConduitPayloadNotVecError
  |~~ `::conduit[вЂ¦]` payload must be a Vec; a non-Vec payload raises this error. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ConduitArityInvalidError
  |~~ `::conduit[вЂ¦]` payload Vec must have either 2 elements (`[params body]`) or 3 elements (`[:self params body]`). ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ConduitBodyNotQuoteError
  |~~ `::conduit` body slot must be a Quote-value carrying the body source. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ConduitParamNotKeywordError
  |~~ `::conduit` params Vec must contain only Keywords; one element is some other type. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ConduitParamsNotVecError
  |~~ `::conduit` params slot must be a Vec of Keywords. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ConduitSelfNameNotKeywordError
  |~~ `::conduit` self-name (3-element payload form) must be a Keyword. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::NullsFirstKeysNotComparableError
  |~~ Operands of `nullsFirst` are not pairwise-comparable scalars. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::NullsLastKeysNotComparableError
  |~~ Operands of `nullsLast` are not pairwise-comparable scalars. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}

::ReifyArityOverflowError
  |~~ `reify` accepts 0 or 1 captured arguments, not more. ~~|
  {:qlang/kind :type}
